- if @advertising_event.try(:enabled)
  %div#home-page-background
    = image_tag(@advertising_event.home_page_background.url)
  %div
    = link_to t('advertising_event.facebook_sign_in'), "http://#{request.host}:#{request.port}/auth/facebook?scope=email&advertising_event_id=#{@advertising_event.id}", class: 'btn btn-primary', id: 'facebook-sign-in'
- else
  Sự kiện đã tạm dừng. Xin vui lòng quay trở lại sau.